Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  海好壮观的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四面全都是水的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  那么兴奋干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰德  那张音谱盘的内容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎在做有关同位体的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  还记载了洛列莱的音素频率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛列莱是第七音素的意识集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音素聚集一定的量之后  据说会拥有自我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是洛列莱的存在还没有被观测到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前只是假设「它是存在的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的音素频率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是任何物质都会发出的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和指纹一样  每一种物质都各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而同位体就是两个音素频率完全相同的个体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是同位体只能通过人为制造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前被研究过的复写技术的话  应该能制造同位体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:37.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(500,500)}（复写技术(フォミクリー)：在理论上能制造同位体的技术，但一直未能成功制成完美的同位体）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是用来制造仿制品的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音素频率会改变  造不出同位体的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事家教没告诉过你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失忆是七年前的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还有一大堆东西要记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要记什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像说话啊  还有父母的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎把你的失忆想得太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯茨尔方向出现不明谱业反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(500,500)}（谱业：以音素为原动力的机械装置）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野蛮的猴子们都聚在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「你这家伙」  给我好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷的美名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是神讬之盾六神将之一  蔷薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是鼻涕虫迪斯特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇！蔷——薇——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蔷薇迪斯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死神迪斯特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同是神讬之盾骑士团的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  那个阴险的杰德曾经可是我天才迪斯特的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪个杰德啊  口味居然这么重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  一生气鼻涕就流下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才~不会流下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人不记小人过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  乖乖地把音谱盘交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你吧  因为内容我全部都记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我当猴耍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我特制超豪华的一招  好好反省下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现身吧  恺撒迪斯特R
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  快散开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有效果的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这招如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFGHSGothicG-W5\fs28}荒れ狂う流れよ！  スプラッシュ{\r}\N疯狂汹涌的水流啊  水柱！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械不防水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪斯特  连你也听从亚修的命令行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那男人没这么容易被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着堪比小强的生命力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然外面的世界好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体…不由自主…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让吾看看  与吾同等之力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在控制我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  冷静下来  深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就这样慢慢将意识集中到双手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  好好听我说的话  就这样放松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发动超振动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅  我究竟怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…对自己被软禁有没有过疑问？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为父亲大人他们担心我的安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是为了把你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界独一无二的  能单独发动超振动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养在基姆拉斯卡一直到死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振动能将一切物质破坏后重新构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是需要两名第七音谱术士才能发动的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一个人就能发动它…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  只要训练  便能在战争中发挥重要作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法布雷公爵和国王都知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我是被当作兵器而软禁的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  至今为止是  以后也会是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  我才不要这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被关在家里  一旦发生战争还要被当成兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点  卢克  总之首先要阻止战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将你这次的功绩公诸于世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让人们承认你是保护了和平的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有自信  你是被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振动的力量将会助你成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------BPART-------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能平安归来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是基姆拉斯卡·兰帕蒂亚王国军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一师团师团长  戈德堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是塞西尔少将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  下面由我来带大家去王城  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的城市  好高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃惊的说  有奇格尔森林的好几倍大的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有回家的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  你失去记忆之后从来没出来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  即使不记得  现在去了解就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅是不是太温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在陛下正在谒见大咏师摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大咏师摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他对叔父大人灌输奇怪的思想之前赶快进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔库特帝国正在加强首都格兰克库玛的防御
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将安格布作为补给据点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  你终于平安回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是导师伊昂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许久不见了  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下正寻找您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩斯  有话待会儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  这位是皮奥尼九世陛下的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰德·卡提斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我国君主向伟大的英戈贝尔特六世陛下送来了亲笔信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父大人  摩斯完全是在胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  我只是把马尔库特的威胁向陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  你明明就是想引发战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有亲笔信  我们也不会无视它的存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了  叔父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  谢谢你  多亏了你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  要我认真起来  这只是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多亏一个好爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话不要老带着刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这真是失礼了  实际上的确是帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来战争就不会发生了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来开始探讨这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我去看看母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮丝想看看卢克大人的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很普通的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的家吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好…好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  还有格兰兹谣将  你们平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯  你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位使者也请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵大人  国王在等您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说卢克这次的遭遇都是拜您所赐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么态度  知道我有多担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  娜塔利娅公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克大人只是在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是和你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出发找卢克之前先到我这儿来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我和卢克结婚之后  你可也是我的佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜塔利娅公主是卢克大人的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个了  你赶快到伯母那儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失踪之后  她病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来探望她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去见她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在意的话  蒂娅你也去向夫人道个歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  真的是卢克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人  请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是梵的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:15:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全因为我想要杀死兄长  才连累了令郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么这次事件并非是有人图谋不轨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我向洛列莱和尤利娅发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅小姐  你还是打消杀掉亲生哥哥的念头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹相残实在是一件很可悲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人病倒了是因为她本来身子就很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大咏师摩斯  您的愿望至今未变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了一些让人在意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说摩斯大人企盼基姆拉斯卡与马尔库特的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱有这种无聊的疑问  去找第七谱石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天会派你去某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克大人  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上国王陛下派使者传话  请您登城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我们决定与马尔库特帝国缔结和平条约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  那么战争就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  缔结条约前还有要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲笔信中除了和平提议外  还有救援的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马尔库特帝国有个叫亚库泽留斯的矿山城市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于大地之毒素  瘴气  而陷入了毁灭的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:18:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔库特方面由于瘴气的阻碍  无法前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若是经由我国的话便能前去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和我有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下希望你能作为亲善大使前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？才不要呢  我不想再惹麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说  卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务有着你必须去的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把谱石拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是落在我国境内的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤利娅·朱耶的第六谱石的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂娅  咏诵一下谱石下方记载的预言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ND2000
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承洛列莱力量之人  生于基姆拉斯卡王国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其人乃继承王族之血的红发男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名曰「圣焰之光」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全听不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是指卢克你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「卢克」在古代伊斯帕尼亚语中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「圣焰之光」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将带领基姆拉斯卡·兰帕蒂亚走向新的繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ND2018
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承洛列莱力量的青年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带领人们前往矿山城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的预言丢失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  这下你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你软禁到现在只是无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在正是你成为英雄之时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然师傅说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的决心  让凯同行照顾你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛列莱教团希望让蒂娅和梵同行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  我也作为使者一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经告诉过你不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事一旦成功  我就能一夜成名做英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅  这是个好机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克  你听我说  那个预言还有下文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下文？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年的力量将是祸患  成为基姆拉斯卡的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教团的上层人物认为你会带来战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤利娅的预言一次都没有出过错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那师傅刚才为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个办法可以阻止战争  同时给你自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言说  你带着亚库泽留斯的人民移动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果引发了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要疏散居民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用超振动中和瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后跟我逃亡到达特就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我这儿  成为神讬之盾骑士团的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能去师傅那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不知道能不能发动超振动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你的  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事不能跟任何人说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被基姆拉斯卡的人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有让你逃亡的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅为什么对我那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  年少时说过要跟我一起去达特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超振动研究中接受了很过分的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对师傅这么说的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以我劫走了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在七年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是师傅你绑架我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会失手  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次被人需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有师傅一直都真心待我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟师傅一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么走吧  去抓住你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
